snippet.title: Witchmarsh - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
205% FUNDED, THANK YOU!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1027299776/witchmarsh

Late to the party? Late backer pledging is still available.

https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=YS8E3T2KXNG5C

Donate the following amounts to get your hands on the game when it's released in December 2015.

£10 - Base Copy of the game

Add the following amounts for these extra rewards, see KS page for details.

£5 - Copy of the soundtrack. Delivered in December 2015.
£5 - Extras, PDF and beta access. (TBA)
£5 - Digital Bestiary
£8 - Extra copies of the game to play with friends.

Thank you.
